Canonical website:
  https://github.com/zapping-vbi/zvbi/

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/zapping-vbi/zvbi/archive/refs/tags/v0.2.44.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack zvbi-0.2.44-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./zvbi-0.2.44-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/zvbi-0.2.44-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/zvbi-0.2.44-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libzvbi0-0.2.44-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libzvbi-devel-0.2.44-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

